# Tests, reports, and files not needed in any image build context.
# NOTE: globs here are non-recursive — `*.md` strips only root-level docs,
# preserving nested assets like apps/web/public/icons/grades/README.md.
# Do NOT exclude scripts/ or apps/web/drizzle/ — the migrate service needs them.
